                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">From the historic row houses along O and P Streets to the commercial properties along Wisconsin Avenue and M Street, our licensed professionals understand the delicate balance between preserving architectural integrity and integrating modern electrical systems. We work closely with the Old Georgetown Board and historic preservation authorities to ensure all electrical work complies with preservation standards.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Our Georgetown electricians are experts in concealed wiring techniques, period-appropriate fixtures, and preservation-compliant upgrades that maintain the character of your historic property while providing the functionality and safety of modern electrical systems.</p>
